Package: DivInsight
Type: Package
Title: Diversity Index Calculation & Visualisation for Taxa and Location
Version: 0.1.0
Author: James Churchward
Maintainer: James Churchward <jameschurchward1@outlook.com>
Description: The functions in the DivInsight package can be used to repurpose occurrence data for calculating diversity index values, creating visuals, and generating species composition matrices for a chosen taxon and location.
